# Opportunities Page Overhaul — Implementation Plan

Overhaul the job scraper backend and frontend Opportunities page to support a wider array of job sources with more reliable scraping methods, and modernize the UI for a premium experience.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Playwright Removal**: The plan proposes **replacing** the Playwright-based Naukri and Indeed scrapers with lighter httpx-based alternatives. Naukri and Indeed have heavy anti-bot protection, so the httpx versions may return fewer results. Do you want to keep Playwright as a fallback option, or fully remove it?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **API Keys**: Two existing scrapers (Adzuna, Reed) use API keys. The new **JSearch (RapidAPI)** scraper is optional and also requires a key. Should we skip JSearch entirely, or add it with a graceful no-key fallback like the others?

> [!WARNING]
> **Remotive Terms of Service**: Remotive's API should not be called more than 4 times/day. Our 30-min cache TTL would call it ~48 times/day on heavy usage. The plan increases cache TTL to 60 minutes and adds per-source rate limiting to stay compliant.

