## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 1. **Playwright removal** — Should we fully remove the Playwright dependency, or keep it as an optional fallback for Naukri/Indeed? Removing it saves ~500MB in Docker image size.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 2. **JSearch (RapidAPI)** — Worth adding as an optional Tier 3 API-keyed scraper? It aggregates from Google Jobs and can pull from many sources, but requires a RapidAPI key.

3. **Background refresh** — Should we add a periodic background task (e.g. every 60 min) that pre-fills the cache, instead of only refreshing on user requests? This would make first-load instant.

4. **Company logos** — Should we try to fetch real company logos (e.g. from Clearbit Logo API `https://logo.clearbit.com/{domain}`) or stick with emoji/letter avatars?

